<h2 className="whyHead">Why should we care?</h2>


        <p>Along this journey, rainwater can turn into stormwater... stormwater needs to be soaked to protect the CAW.</p>

                  <p className="p5">
            We need to allow the stormwater to soak so that it is naturally
            filtered along it's journey through the Central Asheville Watershed
            and into our streams and rivers.
          </p>


               <p>
        Answer the following questions to figure out how you can contribute.
      </p>

      <p>
        This survey is an extension of an on-site survey of the Central
        Asheville Watershed conducted by Lenoir-Rhyne University's
        Sustainability Studies' graduate program.
      </p>